              <span slot="content">Scary movie is a movie directed by Keenen Ivory Wayans. It’s a parody of Scream, the horror movie. This film stars great actor like Dave Sheridan or Shawn Wayans. There is many main characters, all friends in high school. A group of teenagers is chased by a mysterious killer after hiding a deadly accident, and we get fastly into it. The plot is very obvious, but that’s why it’s really funny. The movie has a really cheap production with bad CGI, but that’s also why it’s laughable. The photography of the movie want’s to be good but it’s missed on purpose, and that’s also why it’s laughable. It’s a parody, so the acting is really poor, again on purpose. It’s not natural or stunning at all! The plot is really confusing, and it’s again on purpose but it’s hilarious. Generally, I find this movie quite funny and fascinating. I recommend to watch this movie with friends or family, so you can all laugh together. If you haven’t seen it yet, you’re missing a chance to laugh.</span>
